{
  "video_id": "z1KJAXM3xYA",
  "title": "Amber Case: We are all cyborgs now",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 17259.0,
      "text": "I would like to tell you all"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17260.0,
      "end_time": 20260.0,
      "text": "that you are all actually cyborgs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21260.0,
      "end_time": 23260.0,
      "text": "but not the cyborgs that you think."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23260.0,
      "end_time": 26260.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re not RoboCop, and you&#39;re not Terminator,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26260.0,
      "end_time": 28260.0,
      "text": "but you&#39;re cyborgs every time you look at a computer screen"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28260.0,
      "end_time": 31260.0,
      "text": "or use one of your cell phone devices."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31260.0,
      "end_time": 33260.0,
      "text": "So what&#39;s a good definition for cyborg?"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 33260.0,
      "end_time": 35260.0,
      "text": "Well, traditional definition is \"an organism"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35260.0,
      "end_time": 37260.0,
      "text": "to which exogenous components have been added"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37260.0,
      "end_time": 39260.0,
      "text": "for the purpose of adapting to new environments.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39260.0,
      "end_time": 42260.0,
      "text": "That came from a 1960 paper on space travel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42260.0,
      "end_time": 44260.0,
      "text": "because, if you think about it, space is pretty awkward."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44260.0,
      "end_time": 46260.0,
      "text": "People aren&#39;t supposed to be there."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46260.0,
      "end_time": 49260.0,
      "text": "But humans are curious, and they like to add things to their bodies"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 49260.0,
      "end_time": 51260.0,
      "text": "so they can go to the Alps one day"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 51260.0,
      "end_time": 53260.0,
      "text": "and then become a fish in the sea the next."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 53260.0,
      "end_time": 56260.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s look at the concept of traditional anthropology."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 56260.0,
      "end_time": 58260.0,
      "text": "Somebody goes to another country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 58260.0,
      "end_time": 61260.0,
      "text": "says, \"How fascinating these people are, how interesting their tools are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 61260.0,
      "end_time": 63260.0,
      "text": "how curious their culture is.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 63260.0,
      "end_time": 66259.0,
      "text": "And then they write a paper, and maybe a few other anthropologists read it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 66260.0,
      "end_time": 68260.0,
      "text": "and we think it&#39;s very exotic."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 68260.0,
      "end_time": 71260.0,
      "text": "Well, what&#39;s happening"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 71260.0,
      "end_time": 74260.0,
      "text": "is that we&#39;ve suddenly found a new species."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 74260.0,
      "end_time": 76260.0,
      "text": "I, as a cyborg anthropologist, have suddenly said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 76260.0,
      "end_time": 79260.0,
      "text": "\"Oh, wow. Now suddenly we&#39;re a new form of Homo sapiens,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 79260.0,
      "end_time": 81260.0,
      "text": "and look at these fascinating cultures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 81260.0,
      "end_time": 83260.0,
      "text": "and look at these curious rituals"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 83260.0,
      "end_time": 85260.0,
      "text": "that everybody&#39;s doing around this technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 85260.0,
      "end_time": 88260.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re clicking on things and staring at screens.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 88260.0,
      "end_time": 90260.0,
      "text": "Now there&#39;s a reason why I study this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 90260.0,
      "end_time": 92260.0,
      "text": "versus traditional anthropology."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 92260.0,
      "end_time": 94260.0,
      "text": "And the reason is that tool use,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 94260.0,
      "end_time": 97260.0,
      "text": "in the beginning -- for thousands and thousands of years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 97260.0,
      "end_time": 100260.0,
      "text": "everything has been a physical modification of self."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 100260.0,
      "end_time": 102260.0,
      "text": "It has helped us to extend our physical selves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 102260.0,
      "end_time": 104260.0,
      "text": "go faster, hit things harder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 104260.0,
      "end_time": 106260.0,
      "text": "and there&#39;s been a limit on that."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 106260.0,
      "end_time": 109260.0,
      "text": "But now what we&#39;re looking at is not an extension of the physical self,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 109260.0,
      "end_time": 111260.0,
      "text": "but an extension of the mental self,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 111260.0,
      "end_time": 113260.0,
      "text": "and because of that, we&#39;re able to travel faster,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 113260.0,
      "end_time": 115260.0,
      "text": "communicate differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 115260.0,
      "end_time": 117260.0,
      "text": "And the other thing that happens"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 117260.0,
      "end_time": 120260.0,
      "text": "is that we&#39;re all carrying around little Mary Poppins technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 120260.0,
      "end_time": 123260.0,
      "text": "We can put anything we want into it, and it doesn&#39;t get heavier,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 123260.0,
      "end_time": 125260.0,
      "text": "and then we can take anything out."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 125260.0,
      "end_time": 127260.0,
      "text": "What does the inside of your computer actually look like?"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 127260.0,
      "end_time": 130259.0,
      "text": "Well, if you print it out, it looks like a thousand pounds of material"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 130258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132260.0,
      "text": "that you&#39;re carrying around all the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 132260.0,
      "end_time": 135260.0,
      "text": "And if you actually lose that information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 135260.0,
      "end_time": 138260.0,
      "text": "it means that you suddenly have this loss in your mind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 138260.0,
      "end_time": 141260.0,
      "text": "that you suddenly feel like something&#39;s missing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 141260.0,
      "end_time": 144260.0,
      "text": "except you aren&#39;t able to see it, so it feels like a very strange emotion."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 144260.0,
      "end_time": 147260.0,
      "text": "The other thing that happens is that you have a second self."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 147260.0,
      "end_time": 149260.0,
      "text": "Whether you like it or not, you&#39;re starting to show up online,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 149260.0,
      "end_time": 151260.0,
      "text": "and people are interacting with your second self"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 151260.0,
      "end_time": 153260.0,
      "text": "when you&#39;re not there."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 153260.0,
      "end_time": 155260.0,
      "text": "And so you have to be careful"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 155260.0,
      "end_time": 157260.0,
      "text": "about leaving your front lawn open,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 157260.0,
      "end_time": 159260.0,
      "text": "which is basically your Facebook wall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 159260.0,
      "end_time": 161260.0,
      "text": "so that people don&#39;t write on it in the middle of the night --"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 161260.0,
      "end_time": 163260.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s very much the equivalent."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 163260.0,
      "end_time": 166260.0,
      "text": "And suddenly we have to start to maintain our second self."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 166260.0,
      "end_time": 168260.0,
      "text": "You have to present yourself in digital life"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 168260.0,
      "end_time": 171260.0,
      "text": "in a similar way that you would in your analog life."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 171260.0,
      "end_time": 174260.0,
      "text": "So, in the same way that you wake up, take a shower and get dressed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 174260.0,
      "end_time": 176260.0,
      "text": "you have to learn to do that for your digital self."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 176260.0,
      "end_time": 178260.0,
      "text": "And the problem is that a lot of people now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 178260.0,
      "end_time": 180260.0,
      "text": "especially adolescents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 180260.0,
      "end_time": 182260.0,
      "text": "have to go through two adolescences."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 182260.0,
      "end_time": 185260.0,
      "text": "They have to go through their primary one, that&#39;s already awkward,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 185260.0,
      "end_time": 187260.0,
      "text": "and then they go through their second self&#39;s adolescence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 187260.0,
      "end_time": 189260.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s even more awkward"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 189260.0,
      "end_time": 192260.0,
      "text": "because there&#39;s an actual history"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 192260.0,
      "end_time": 194260.0,
      "text": "of what they&#39;ve gone through online."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 194260.0,
      "end_time": 196260.0,
      "text": "And anybody coming in new to technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 196260.0,
      "end_time": 198260.0,
      "text": "is an adolescent online right now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 198260.0,
      "end_time": 200260.0,
      "text": "and so it&#39;s very awkward,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 200260.0,
      "end_time": 203260.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s very difficult for them to do those things."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 203260.0,
      "end_time": 205260.0,
      "text": "So when I was little, my dad would sit me down at night and he would say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 205260.0,
      "end_time": 207260.0,
      "text": "\"I&#39;m going to teach you about time and space in the future.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 207260.0,
      "end_time": 209260.0,
      "text": "And I said, \"Great.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 209260.0,
      "end_time": 211260.0,
      "text": "And he said one day, \"What&#39;s the shortest distance between two points?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 211260.0,
      "end_time": 214260.0,
      "text": "And I said, \"Well, that&#39;s a straight line. You told me that yesterday.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 214260.0,
      "end_time": 216260.0,
      "text": "I thought I was very clever."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 216260.0,
      "end_time": 219260.0,
      "text": "He said, \"No, no, no. Here&#39;s a better way.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 219260.0,
      "end_time": 221260.0,
      "text": "He took a piece of paper,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 221260.0,
      "end_time": 223260.0,
      "text": "drew A and B on one side and the other"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 223260.0,
      "end_time": 226260.0,
      "text": "and folded them together so where A and B touched."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 226260.0,
      "end_time": 229260.0,
      "text": "And he said, \"That is the shortest distance between two points.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 229260.0,
      "end_time": 231260.0,
      "text": "And I said, \"Dad, dad, dad, how do you do that?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 231260.0,
      "end_time": 233260.0,
      "text": "He said, \"Well, you just bend time and space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 233260.0,
      "end_time": 235260.0,
      "text": "it takes an awful lot of energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 235260.0,
      "end_time": 237260.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s just how you do it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 237260.0,
      "end_time": 239260.0,
      "text": "And I said, \"I want to do that.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 239260.0,
      "end_time": 241260.0,
      "text": "And he said, \"Well, okay.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 241260.0,
      "end_time": 244260.0,
      "text": "And so, when I went to sleep for the next 10 or 20 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 244260.0,
      "end_time": 246260.0,
      "text": "I was thinking at night,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 246260.0,
      "end_time": 248260.0,
      "text": "\"I want to be the first person to create a wormhole,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 248260.0,
      "end_time": 250260.0,
      "text": "to make things accelerate faster."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 250260.0,
      "end_time": 252260.0,
      "text": "And I want to make a time machine.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 252260.0,
      "end_time": 254260.0,
      "text": "I was always sending messages to my future self"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 254260.0,
      "end_time": 257260.0,
      "text": "using tape recorders."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 259260.0,
      "end_time": 261260.0,
      "text": "But then what I realized when I went to college"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 261260.0,
      "end_time": 263260.0,
      "text": "is that technology doesn&#39;t just get adopted"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 263260.0,
      "end_time": 265260.0,
      "text": "because it works."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 265260.0,
      "end_time": 267260.0,
      "text": "It gets adopted because people use it"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 267260.0,
      "end_time": 269260.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s made for humans."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 269260.0,
      "end_time": 271260.0,
      "text": "So I started studying anthropology."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 271260.0,
      "end_time": 273260.0,
      "text": "And when I was writing my thesis on cell phones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 273260.0,
      "end_time": 276260.0,
      "text": "I realized that everyone was carrying around wormholes in their pockets."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 276260.0,
      "end_time": 278260.0,
      "text": "They weren&#39;t physically transporting themselves;"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 278260.0,
      "end_time": 280260.0,
      "text": "they were mentally transporting themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 280260.0,
      "end_time": 282260.0,
      "text": "They would click on a button,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 282260.0,
      "end_time": 285260.0,
      "text": "and they would be connected as A to B immediately."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 285260.0,
      "end_time": 287260.0,
      "text": "And I thought, \"Oh, wow. I found it. This is great.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 287260.0,
      "end_time": 289260.0,
      "text": "So over time, time and space"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 289260.0,
      "end_time": 291260.0,
      "text": "have compressed because of this."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 291260.0,
      "end_time": 293260.0,
      "text": "You can stand on one side of the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 293260.0,
      "end_time": 295260.0,
      "text": "whisper something and be heard on the other."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 295260.0,
      "end_time": 297260.0,
      "text": "One of the other ideas that comes around"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 297260.0,
      "end_time": 300260.0,
      "text": "is that you have a different type of time on every single device that you use."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 300260.0,
      "end_time": 303260.0,
      "text": "Every single browser tab gives you a different type of time."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 303260.0,
      "end_time": 305260.0,
      "text": "And because of that, you start to dig around"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 305260.0,
      "end_time": 307260.0,
      "text": "for your external memories -- where did you leave them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 307260.0,
      "end_time": 309260.0,
      "text": "So now we&#39;re all these paleontologists"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 309260.0,
      "end_time": 311260.0,
      "text": "that are digging for things that we&#39;ve lost"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 311260.0,
      "end_time": 314260.0,
      "text": "on our external brains that we&#39;re carrying around in our pockets."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 314260.0,
      "end_time": 316260.0,
      "text": "And that incites a sort of panic architecture --"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 316260.0,
      "end_time": 318260.0,
      "text": "\"Oh no, where&#39;s this thing?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 318260.0,
      "end_time": 321260.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re all \"I Love Lucy\" on a great assembly line of information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 321260.0,
      "end_time": 323260.0,
      "text": "and we can&#39;t keep up."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 324260.0,
      "end_time": 326260.0,
      "text": "And so what happens is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 326260.0,
      "end_time": 328260.0,
      "text": "when we bring all that into the social space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 328260.0,
      "end_time": 330260.0,
      "text": "we end up checking our phones all the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 330260.0,
      "end_time": 332260.0,
      "text": "So we have this thing called ambient intimacy."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 332260.0,
      "end_time": 334260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not that we&#39;re always connected to everybody,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 334260.0,
      "end_time": 337260.0,
      "text": "but at anytime we can connect to anyone we want."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 337260.0,
      "end_time": 339260.0,
      "text": "And if you were able to print out everybody in your cell phone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 339260.0,
      "end_time": 341260.0,
      "text": "the room would be very crowded."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 341260.0,
      "end_time": 344260.0,
      "text": "These are the people that you have access to right now, in general --"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 344260.0,
      "end_time": 347260.0,
      "text": "all of these people, all of your friends and family that you can connect to."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 347260.0,
      "end_time": 350260.0,
      "text": "And so there are some psychological effects that happen with this."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 350260.0,
      "end_time": 352260.0,
      "text": "One I&#39;m really worried about"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 352260.0,
      "end_time": 355260.0,
      "text": "is that people aren&#39;t taking time for mental reflection anymore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 355260.0,
      "end_time": 357260.0,
      "text": "and that they aren&#39;t slowing down and stopping,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 357260.0,
      "end_time": 359260.0,
      "text": "being around all those people in the room all the time"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 359260.0,
      "end_time": 361260.0,
      "text": "that are trying to compete for their attention"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 361260.0,
      "end_time": 363260.0,
      "text": "on the simultaneous time interfaces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 363260.0,
      "end_time": 365260.0,
      "text": "paleontology and panic architecture."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 365260.0,
      "end_time": 367260.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re not just sitting there."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 367260.0,
      "end_time": 370260.0,
      "text": "And really, when you have no external input,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 370260.0,
      "end_time": 372260.0,
      "text": "that is a time when there is a creation of self,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 372260.0,
      "end_time": 374260.0,
      "text": "when you can do long-term planning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 374260.0,
      "end_time": 377260.0,
      "text": "when you can try and figure out who you really are."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 377260.0,
      "end_time": 379260.0,
      "text": "And then, once you do that, you can figure out"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 379260.0,
      "end_time": 381260.0,
      "text": "how to present your second self in a legitimate way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 381260.0,
      "end_time": 383260.0,
      "text": "instead of just dealing with everything as it comes in --"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 383260.0,
      "end_time": 386260.0,
      "text": "and oh, I have to do this, and I have to do this, and I have to do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 386260.0,
      "end_time": 388260.0,
      "text": "And so this is very important."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 388260.0,
      "end_time": 390260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m really worried that, especially kids today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 390260.0,
      "end_time": 393260.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re not going to be dealing with this down-time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 393260.0,
      "end_time": 395260.0,
      "text": "that they have an instantaneous button-clicking culture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 395260.0,
      "end_time": 397260.0,
      "text": "and that everything comes to them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 397260.0,
      "end_time": 400260.0,
      "text": "and that they become very excited about it and very addicted to it."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 400260.0,
      "end_time": 403260.0,
      "text": "So if you think about it, the world hasn&#39;t stopped either."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 403260.0,
      "end_time": 405260.0,
      "text": "It has its own external prosthetic devices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 405260.0,
      "end_time": 407260.0,
      "text": "and these devices are helping us all"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 407260.0,
      "end_time": 409260.0,
      "text": "to communicate and interact with each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 409260.0,
      "end_time": 411260.0,
      "text": "But when you actually visualize it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 411260.0,
      "end_time": 413260.0,
      "text": "all the connections that we&#39;re doing right now --"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 413260.0,
      "end_time": 416260.0,
      "text": "this is an image of the mapping of the Internet --"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 416260.0,
      "end_time": 418260.0,
      "text": "it doesn&#39;t look technological."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 418260.0,
      "end_time": 420260.0,
      "text": "It actually looks very organic."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 420260.0,
      "end_time": 423260.0,
      "text": "This is the first time in the entire history of humanity"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 423260.0,
      "end_time": 425260.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;ve connected in this way."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 426260.0,
      "end_time": 429260.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s not that machines are taking over."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 429260.0,
      "end_time": 431260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s that they&#39;re helping us to be more human,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 431260.0,
      "end_time": 433260.0,
      "text": "helping us to connect with each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 433260.0,
      "end_time": 436260.0,
      "text": "The most successful technology gets out of the way"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 436260.0,
      "end_time": 438260.0,
      "text": "and helps us live our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 438260.0,
      "end_time": 440260.0,
      "text": "And really,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 440260.0,
      "end_time": 443260.0,
      "text": "it ends up being more human than technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 443260.0,
      "end_time": 445260.0,
      "text": "because we&#39;re co-creating each other all the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 445260.0,
      "end_time": 448260.0,
      "text": "And so this is the important point that I like to study:"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 448260.0,
      "end_time": 451260.0,
      "text": "that things are beautiful, that it&#39;s still a human connection --"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 451260.0,
      "end_time": 453260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s just done in a different way."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 453260.0,
      "end_time": 455260.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re just increasing our humanness"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 455260.0,
      "end_time": 458260.0,
      "text": "and our ability to connect with each other, regardless of geography."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 458260.0,
      "end_time": 460260.0,
      "text": "So that&#39;s why I study cyborg anthropology."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 460260.0,
      "end_time": 462260.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 462260.0,
      "end_time": 466260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}